            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VcaKajYRxd3aV2epmBUGcw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEB8R0JA_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周四，2月26日，美股開市前，美股指期貨普跌，納指100期貨跌0.11%，道指30期貨跌0.17%，標普500期貨跌0.11%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"195\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CSTkpZFYtKyrP0rNfa1ODQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTE5NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/09503aa16742287931249672786e9d1e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">XAU/USD小幅拉升，現報5177.64美元，XAG/USD跌超2%，現報87.37美元。原油微跌，美油現報65.32美元，布油現報70.62美元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"658\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dFATPqzX5T36t_hmhx.72g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExMDQ-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/8c2f0be6979034863a9fcce183daaa69\" width=\"572\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">人民幣對美元匯率持續走高，在岸、離岸人民幣對美元匯率雙雙升破6.84關口，創近三年新高。分析師指出，短期內美元指數大幅反彈的可能性較小，預計春節後一段時間人民幣還會處在一個偏強運行狀態。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6df2e1e9-fb71-3770-be68-b0a200278da6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"581\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YpKQzhzH_eCftkaq1zlhtQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/63f3df391ce06eb5e6a69a95c6012d05\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eXAKWL1zkNAAn8Tafcy6fQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/b3e15893366523d54b1dcfd4747513b2\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">比特幣 (BitfinexUSD)反彈升近4%，現報6.8萬美元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZfPZAcsz7cyxv2EEBMqtlw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/7ed3d2d9bdcd5be212bfcc773b3e6128\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>英偉達財報一鍵解讀，</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>助您尋找市場機會，</span